            <title>[SPARK-23148] spark.read.csv with multiline=true gives FileNotFoundException if path contains spaces</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-23148</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Repro code:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
spark.range(10).write.csv(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/tmp/a b c/a.csv&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
spark.read.option(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;multiLine&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;).csv(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/tmp/a b c/a.csv&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).count
10
