java.io.FileNotFoundException: File file:/tmp/a%20b%20c/a.csv/part-00000-cf84f9b2-5fe6-4f54-a130-a1737689db00-c000.csv does not exist
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Trying to manually escape fails in a different place:&lt;/p&gt;
