                            <comment id="17023935" author="jomach" created="Sun, 26 Jan 2020 21:28:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hyukjin.kwon&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;hyukjin.kwon&quot;&gt;hyukjin.kwon&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=henryr&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;henryr&quot;&gt;henryr&lt;/a&gt; &#160;, I have the same problem if I create a custom data source&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

